              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "body": "Hi Vrushali, FYI, we have an integration test inside TestDistributedShell (search for v2). Once you have the POC backend impl and wire aggregator to it, you can use this test case to verify the POC prototye work properly. So far we have seen that distributed shell app can write new timeline entity to the per node aggregator, and it has been routed the right per app aggregator. You may start from there.",
